---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Load Testing">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Know Your Application's Handling Capacity</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies Load Testing Service helps you gauge the capacity of any software application before deployment — preventing severe bottlenecks by running the full load testing process with ordered phases, virtual users and real diagnostic tools.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-users"></i></div>
            <h5>Scalable User Testing</h5>
            <p>Test with an increasing number of virtual users to understand exactly how your application behaves under growing load.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-server"></i></div>
            <h5>Hardware Planning</h5>
            <p>Plan additional resource and hardware requirements by understanding real-world capacity limits before they become problems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-cog"></i></div>
            <h5>Efficient Hardware Use</h5>
            <p>Ensure effective use of existing hardware for the specified load, avoiding over-provisioning and unnecessary infrastructure spend.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-list-ol"></i></div>
            <h5>Ordered Test Phases</h5>
            <p>A complete load testing process with clearly ordered phases — from baseline through peak load to recovery — for reliable results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bug"></i></div>
            <h5>Bottleneck Isolation</h5>
            <p>Modern virtual gear and techniques for faster load testing, with precise isolation and identification of performance bottlenecks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-stethoscope"></i></div>
            <h5>Diagnostic Analysis</h5>
            <p>Wide range of analysis components and diagnostic software to identify the root cause of issues discovered during load runs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
